reviewText: I don't like it. It's a play.

I though this series was going to be good for me to have more christian movies to look at.  But this series has failed to live up to it's NAME...KEEPIN THE FAITH.

Bad acting by all. They must have pulled these people off the street to make this movie and the  others.

Did not like it. Look for more depth,substance. Some scenes did not connect with others.

I'm angry I bought these movies. Won't buy anymore.,
